<spacer length="12"/>

<para>
It is also possible to specify more than one column by using a list
with more than one item in it. If we used ('[2,3]'), the tmatrix would return:</para>
<codesnippet language="python">((17, 19, 13), (25, 28, 20))</codesnippet>

